Package org.wmn4j.io.musicxml

Interface MusicXmlWriter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ScoreWriter
    public interface MusicXmlWriter
extends ScoreWriter
    Represents a writer for MusicXML files.

    Implementations of this interface are not guaranteed to be thread-safe.

        static MusicXmlWriter writerFor​(java.util.Collection<Pattern> patterns)
        Returns an instance of a writer for the given Pattern collection.

        The patterns are written into MusicXML so that they are separated by double bar lines and system breaks from each other.
